===Noun===
'''pluck'''  {{uncountable}}

# [[nerve]], [[fortitude]], or [[persistence]]
#:''He didn't get far with the attempt, but you have to admire his '''pluck'''.''

====Translations====
*Catalan: [[perseverància]] {{f}}
*Dutch: [[doorzettingsvermogen]] {{n}}
